### Health
GET http://localhost:5050/api/health

### Register
# @name register
POST http://localhost:5050/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@mail.mcgill.ca",
  "password": "Demo1234",
  "displayName": "Demo User"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:5050/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@mail.mcgill.ca",
  "password": "Demo1234"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Me
GET http://localhost:5050/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List courses
GET http://localhost:5050/api/courses?search=COMP

### Create course (catalog-validated; auto-fills name + faculty)
POST http://localhost:5050/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "COMP 424"
}

### Create course — expect 404 not_in_catalog
POST http://localhost:5050/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "FAKE 999"
}

### Delete course — admin only (replace COURSE_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5050/api/courses/COURSE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### My courses
GET http://localhost:5050/api/me/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Enroll (replace COURSE_ID)
POST http://localhost:5050/api/courses/COURSE_ID/enroll
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create post
POST http://localhost:5050/api/courses/COURSE_ID/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "How to approach assignment 2?",
  "body": "Anyone understood the recursion question? Here's my attempt:\n\n```js\nfunction fib(n){\n  if(n<2) return n;\n  return fib(n-1)+fib(n-2);\n}\n```"
}

### List posts (latest)
GET http://localhost:5050/api/courses/COURSE_ID/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List posts (hot)
GET http://localhost:5050/api/courses/COURSE_ID/posts?sort=hot
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Single post
GET http://localhost:5050/api/posts/POST_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Like
POST http://localhost:5050/api/posts/POST_ID/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Unlike
DELETE http://localhost:5050/api/posts/POST_ID/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reply
POST http://localhost:5050/api/posts/POST_ID/replies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "body": "Great question — I had the same one." }

### Activity
GET http://localhost:5050/api/me/activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
